&quot;Of course, everything that is presented to me as an accusation today is all new to me, I am completely unfamiliar with it,&quot; he said.
The court arrested the deputy from United Russia not for ten days before the arraignment, as was the case with previous high-ranking Dagestan officials, but for two months at once, since Art. 210 of the Criminal Code of the Russian Federation.
